  "detailed_description": "Vector Assault is a fast paced twin stick shooter where you have to survive a onslaught of enemy attackers.<br />\r\nThe more enemies you defeat the higher your score will become.  <br />\r\nTry to achieve the highest score possible across multiple game modes, and levels.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features:\t<br />\r\n- Four Game Modes<br />\r\n- Arcade<br />\r\n- Survival<br />\r\n- Weapon Trial<br />\r\n- Time Trial<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- 9 Stages<br />\r\n- Multiple Power-ups<br />\r\n- 3 Playerable Ships<br />\r\n- Challenges/Achievements<br />\r\n- Online Leaderboards<br />\r\n- Xbox One Controller Support",
